About
21 Bars, 3 Cuisines, 1 Beach Club in one unique venue. Offering a day-to-night experience with a breathtaking view of Bluewaters and The Dubai Eye. Located at The Beach, JBR. Under 21 allowed in the restaurant only from 8am to 5pm.
Duration: 2-3 hours
